dct_title_s: A topographical map of the Monmouth shore : with the interior from Metuchen to Lakewood
dct_description_sm: In upper margin: Geological Survey of New Jersey. Atlas sheet no. 9 (Monmouth Shore). Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Depths shown by isolines. "From original surveys and levelings based on the triangulation of the U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey."
dct_publisher_sm: [Trenton, N.J.] : Geological Survey of New Jersey, 1902.
